%3EAttorneys%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flisa-cook-federal-reserve-tro-hearing-trump-doj-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve%20Governor%20Lisa%20Cook%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20denying%20allegations%20that%20the%20key%20Fed%20official%20committed%20mortgage%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Tuesday%20filing%2C%20Cook's%20attorneys%20submitted%20additional%20arguments%20in%20support%20of%20a%20request%20for%20a%20temporary%20restraining%20order%20that%20would%20block%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fire-fed-governor-lisa-cook-means-inflation-interest-rates-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E's%20attempt%20to%20oust%20a%20key%20member%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attorneys%20said%20in%20the%2031-page%20filing%20that%20Cook%20didn't%20receive%20proper%20due%20process%2C%20including%20an%20opportunity%20to%20address%20the%20allegations%20made%20against%20her%2C%20and%20the%20justification%20for%20her%20firing%20wouldn't%20rise%20to%20the%20level%20of%20%26quot%3Bfor%20cause%26quot%3B%20removal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSetting%20aside%20the%20fact%20that%20Governor%20Cook%20did%20not%20ever%20commit%20mortgage%20fraud%2C%20any%20such%20pre-office%20offense%20plainly%20would%20not%20have%20been%20'so%20infamous%20a%20nature%2C%20as%20to%20render%20the%20offender%20unfit%20to%20execute%20any%20public%20franchise%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20attorneys%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20and%20attorneys%20for%20Cook%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2020%2C%20Bill%20Pulte%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Federal%20Housing%20Finance%20Agency%2C%20published%20a%20letter%20on%20X%20that%20accused%20Cook%20of%20falsifying%20bank%20documents%20and%20property%20records%20to%20secure%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20favorable%26quot%3B%20mortgage.%20In%20particular%2C%20Pulte%20says%20Cook%20improperly%20designated%20which%20of%20her%20homes%20served%20as%20a%20primary%20and%20secondary%20place%20of%20residence%20while%20filing%20paperwork%20for%20a%20home%20loan%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook's%20attorneys%20said%20in%20the%20Tuesday%20filing%20that%20Trump%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-says-removed-key-fed-official-governor-lisa-cook-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20Cook's%20removal%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20account%20half%20an%20hour%20after%20Pulte's%20social%20media%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernor%20Cook%20learned%20of%20these%20developments%20only%20through%20the%20grapevine%20%E2%80%94%20no%20government%20official%20gave%20her%20notice%20of%20these%20Truth%20Social%20posts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20attorneys%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook's%20attorneys%20called%20the%20claims%20%26quot%3Balleged%20facial%20inconsistencies%26quot%3B%20that%20were%20already%20disclosed%20to%20the%20government%20during%20the%20vetting%20and%20confirmation%20process.%20Cook%20was%20nominated%20by%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Senate%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20alleged%20inconsistencies%2C%20attorneys%20wrote%2C%20do%20not%20rise%20to%20the%20level%20of%20%26quot%3Bfor%20cause%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20Humphrey's%20Executor%2C%20a%201935%20landmark%20Supreme%20Court%20case%20that%20established%20how%20a%20sitting%20US%20president%20cannot%20fire%20officials%20of%20an%20independent%20agency%20based%20on%20policy%20or%20political%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2025%2C%20Trump%20posted%20a%20termination%20letter%20on%20Truth%20Social%20that%20was%20addressed%20to%20Cook%2C%20calling%20for%20her%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20removal%20from%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20responded%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20purported%20to%20fire%20me%20'for%20cause'%2