penalties%20if%20not%20for%20generative%20AI's%20rise.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIronically%2C%20Google%20has%20been%20a%20fierce%20OpenAI%20competitor%20after%20it%20was%20upstaged%20by%20ChatGPT%20in%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-antitrust-monopoly-case-decision-winners-losers-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edodged%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20breakup%20of%20some%20of%20its%20key%20businesses%2C%20and%20it%20has%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-antitrust-case-doj-remedy-alphabet-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunlikely%20competitor%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20thank%3A%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20ruled%20Tuesday%20that%20generative%20AI's%20rise%20has%20made%20search%20more%20competitive%2C%20undermining%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20case%20for%20carving%20up%20Google's%20empire%2C%20which%20could%20have%20seen%20products%20like%20YouTube%20or%20Chrome%20become%20totally%20independent%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Judge%20Amit%20Mehta's%20decision%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20generative%20AI%20brought%20about%20by%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20was%20repeatedly%20mentioned%20for%20making%20the%20search%20business%20more%20competitive%20than%20ever.%20That%20weakened%20the%20case%20for%20radically%20restructuring%20Google's%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudge%20Mehta%20wrote%20that%20while%20generative%20AI%20hasn't%20displaced%20Googling%20yet%2C%20AI%20startups%20could%20%26quot%3Bend%20up%20being%20game%20changers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20use%20GenAI%20chatbots%2C%20like%20ChatGPT%2C%20Perplexity%2C%20and%20Anthropic's%20Claude%2C%20to%20gather%20information%20that%20they%20previously%20sought%20through%20internet%20search%2C%20Mehta%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20August%2C%20OpenAI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2025%2F08%2F04%2Fopenai-chatgpt-700-million-users.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20ChatGPT%20is%20set%20to%20hit%20700%20million%20weekly%20active%20users%2C%20up%20from%20500%20million%20in%20March.%20The%20app%20for%20Google's%20answer%20to%20ChatGPT%2C%20Gemini%2C%20had%20450%20million%20monthly%20active%20users%2C%20Google's%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20said%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMehta%20also%20mentioned%20the%20AI%20investment%20boom%20spurred%20by%20ChatGPT%2C%20which%20led%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bastonishing%26quot%3B%20rush%20of%20funding%20for%20AI%20startups%20whose%20products%20directly%20threaten%20traditional%20internet%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20companies%20are%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20position%20to%20compete%20with%20Google%20than%20any%20traditional%20search%20company%20has%20been%20in%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20Mehta%20wrote.%20Plus%2C%20they're%20moving%20quickly%20to%20monetize%20their%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20would%20have%20happened%20had%20OpenAI%20not%20launched%20ChatGPT%20back%20in%202022.%20Funnily%20enough%2C%20ChatGPT's%20launch%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20moment%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-management-issues-code-red-over-chatgpt-report-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Google%2C%20which%20had%20been%20considered%20the%20main%20AI%20powerhouse%20before%20OpenAI's%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20since%20competed%20fiercely%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20launching%20its%20own%20chatbot%2C%20Bard%2C%20shortly%20after%20ChatGPT%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20extensively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-used-chatgpt-to-improve-bard-scale-ai-documents-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusing%20ChatGPT%20to%20improve%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Business%20Insider%20investigation%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20remains%20threatened%20by%20OpenAI's%20new%20style%20of%20discovering%20information.%20In%2