le%20international%20business%20model.%20Now%2C%20the%20league%20is%20betting%20that%20its%20global%20efforts%20can%20succeed%20where%20others%20have%20stalled%2C%20with%20a%20strategy%20built%20on%20business%20partnerships%20and%20cultivating%20local%20fan%20bases%20around%20existing%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20having%20a%20game%20in%20a%20country%20is%20not%20enough%2C%20just%20having%20broadcast%20distribution%20is%20not%20enough%2C%20just%20doing%20social%20is%20not%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20it%20takes%20a%20comprehensive%20plan%20to%20activate%20and%20engage%20fans%20year-round%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gerrit%20Meier%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20and%20head%20of%20NFL%20International.%20%26quot%3BGames%20and%20media%20reach%20are%20key%20catalysts%20here%2C%20but%20they%20need%20the%20support%20of%20many%20other%20tactics%2C%20including%20dedicated%20local%20teams.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c2804bc-dbc6-4f56-ad55-b00fa33c00a9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20targeted%20strategy%20abroad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20driver%20for%20the%20NFL's%20expansion%20abroad%20has%20been%20its%20Global%20Markets%20Program%2C%20which%20gives%20clubs%20international%20marketing%20rights%20to%20specific%20countries.%20Teams%20can%20apply%20for%20rights%20in%20one%20or%20more%20countries%2C%20targeting%20locations%20that%20make%20the%20most%20sense%20from%20both%20a%20cultural%20and%20business%20standpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20program%2C%20teams%20use%20targeted%20strategies%20to%20build%20fandom%20and%20brand%20awareness%20abroad.%20These%20include%20local%20events%20that%20engage%20directly%20with%20fans%2C%20such%20as%20watch%20parties%2C%20and%20encouraging%20participation%20in%20the%20sport%20through%20youth%20football%20clinics%20and%20the%20promotion%20of%20organized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-flag-football-critical-to-nfl-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflag%20football%3C%2Fa%