y%20of%20Kasey%20Kuiper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20after%20graduating%2C%20and%20started%20talking%20to%20me%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-teacher-shares-what-schools-need-keep-teachers-happy-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eworking%20in%20education%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Because%20of%20his%20interest%20in%20things%20like%20working%20out%2C%20power%20lifting%2C%20and%20rock%20climbing%2C%20I%20suggested%20being%20a%20PE%20and%20health%20teacher.%20He%20was%20coaching%20wrestling%20at%20a%20local%20high%20school%20and%20really%20loved%20it%2C%20which%20gave%20him%20confidence%20in%20pursuing%20teaching%20full-time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20PE%20teacher%20at%20the%20school%20I%20was%20working%20at%20quit%20halfway%20through%20the%20year.%20Marcus%20had%20just%20finished%20college%20and%20got%20hired%20as%20the%20replacement.%20A%20lot%20of%20kids%20already%20knew%20who%20he%20was%20and%20that%20we%20were%20dating%20because%20he%20had%20been%20helping%20me%20coach%20some%20of%20the%20sports%20teams%20in%20his%20spare%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1f7a398-9851-4f58-b481-81b118f86430%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20was%20really%20nice%20working%20at%20the%20same%20school%20together%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20didn't%20work%20at%20the%20same%20school%20together%20for%20long%2C%20but%20it%20was%20really%20nice%20when%20we%20did.%20We%20never%20really%20saw%20each%20other%2C%20but%20it%20was%20comforting%20to%20know%20we%20were%20in%20the%20same%20building%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20time%20I%20hurt%20myself%20in%20my%20classroom%20and%20he%20came%20to%20help%20me%20because%20he%20was%20the%20PE%20and%20health%20teacher.%20He%20felt%20responsible%20for%20taking%20care%20of%20me