or%20when%20I%20need%20to%20be%20firmer.%20We%20can%20give%20each%20other%20different%20perspectives%20on%20situations%2C%20too%2C%20which%20is%20helpful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20a%20teacher%20is%20a%20really%20consuming%20job%2C%20but%20we%20have%20a%20rule%20that%20we%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-restored-my-marriage-by-setting-boundaries-about-work-talk-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etry%20not%20to%20talk%20about%20work%20when%20we're%20home%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We%20both%20work%20about%2045%20minutes%20away%2C%20so%20we%20call%20each%20other%20on%20our%20way%20back%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20day.%20It%20gives%20us%20an%20opportunity%20to%20vent%2C%20but%20then%20we%20leave%20it%20in%20the%20car.%20At%20home%2C%20sometimes%20I'll%20need%20to%20grade%20papers%2C%20but%20other%20than%20that%2C%20we%20really%20try%20to%20have%20a%20clear%20work-life%20separation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236983c50-9d8f-433f-98ac-e643af44222e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20would%20work%20at%20the%20same%20school%20as%20my%20husband%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20work%20together%20again%2C%20but%20we%20both%20really%20love%20our%20schools%20and%20our%20coworkers.%20We've%20talked%20about%20it%2C%20and%20for%20now%20we're%20going%20to%20stay%20in%20our%20districts.%20But%20we're%20expecting%20our%20first%20child%20in%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20and%20maybe%20in%20the%20future%20we'll%20want%20to%20have%20a%20shorter%20commute%20and%20be%20closer%20to%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Couple%20posing%20for%20photo%20pregnancy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b7442aa17a8c5b4053e0c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20is%20expecting%20their%20first%20child%20tog