0%26quot%3Btip%26quot%3B%20on%20social%20media%20may%20be%20less%20concrete%20than%20on%20a%20bar%20tab%20or%20restaurant%20check.%20Most%20social-media%20platforms%20offer%20some%20form%20of%20tipping%20under%20various%20names.%20On%20Twitch%2C%20they're%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bbits.%26quot%3B%20On%20TikTok%2C%20they're%20called%20%26quot%3Bgifts%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20on%20YouTube%2C%20they're%20%26quot%3BSuper%20Chats.%26quot%3B%20Tipping%20is%20common%20on%20OnlyFans%2C%20where%20creators%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-onlyfans-creators-make-price-tip-menus-examples-templates-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoffer%20%26quot%3Btip%20menus%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20viewers%20to%20pay%20for%20custom%20content%20or%20video%20chatting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdemocrats-no-tax-tips-senate-passage-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNo%20tax%20on%20tips%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20one%20of%20Trump's%20key%20economic%20campaign%20pledges%20during%20the%202024%20campaign%2C%20and%20was%20one%20of%20several%20key%20changes%20to%20the%20tax%20code%20included%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-big-beautiful-bill-impacts-wallet-taxes-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Congress%20passed%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20law%2C%20workers%20in%20occupations%20that%20%26quot%3Bcustomarily%20and%20regularly%26quot%3B%20receive%20tips%20will%20be%20eligible%20to%20claim%20a%20deduction%20for%20those%20tips%20up%20to%20%2425%2C000.%20That%20deduction%20gradually%20phases%20out%20for%20individuals%20making%20more%20than%20%24150%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20or%20a%20married%20couple%20making%20%24300%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20earners%20on%20T