%20understand%20the%20syllabus%20and%20test%20myself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20his%20own%20surprise%2C%20he%20cleared%20prelims%20in%20his%20very%20first%20attempt.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20gave%20me%20confidence%20that%20self-study%20could%20work%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20mains%20exam%20was%20a%20different%20story%20altogether.%20And%20a%20challenging%20one%20at%20that.%20He%20fell%20short.%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20like%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20study%20enough%20for%20the%20mains.%20Also%2C%20I%20scored%20very%20less%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F460341%2Fharyana-ajay-irs-officer-shares-tips-mistakes-of-selecting-upsc-optional-anthropology-startegy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoptional%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Electrical%20Engineering.%20It%E2%80%99s%20500%20marks.%20I%20realised%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20treat%20it%20casually.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20setback%20at%20the%20mains%20weighed%20on%20him.%20By%20mid-2019%2C%20Subhankar%20made%20a%20big%20decision%20%E2%80%94%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20shifted%20to%20Delhi%20for%20six%20months%20to%20give%20full-time%20preparation%20a%20try.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20went%20all%20in%20on%20his%20optional%2C%20using%20NPTEL%20(National%20Programme%20on%20Technology%20Enhanced%20Learning)%20lectures%2C%20Engineering%20Services%20material%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F477761%2Fwest-bengal-most-women-ias-officers-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E(the%20UPSC%20exam%20for%20engineers)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20countless%20practice%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsubhankar-bala-ias-2-1756804045.jpg%5C%22%20width%3