0Society%2C%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20a%20way%20of%20life.%20In%20fact%2C%20before%20he%20turned%20to%20nature%20conservation%2C%20he%20hunted%20animals%20living%20in%20the%20wild%20with%20his%20family%20and%20friends.%20For%20his%20forefathers%2C%20hunting%20was%20the%20way%20to%20survive%20and%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A494570%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20and%20his%20six%20sons%2C%20including%20my%20father%2C%20migrated%20from%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20early%201950s%20to%20settlements%20like%20Hemnagar%20and%20Kumirmari%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20before%20settling%20on%20Bali%20Island.%20It%20was%20a%20forest%20at%20the%20time%2C%20part%20of%20which%20they%20cut%20down%20to%20establish%20their%20habitat.%20Naturally%2C%20they%20poached%20deer%2C%20tigers%2C%20birds%2C%20wild%20boars%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20wildlife.%20When%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20I%20automatically%20learnt%20how%20to%20hunt%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mistry%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20everything%20changed%20one%20fine%20day%20in%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20graduation%2C%20I%20would%20play%20football%20with%20my%20friends%20and%20then%20hunt%20deer%20for%20pleasure.%20One%20day%2C%20when%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20were%20out%20hunting%2C%20they%20shot%20a%20doe%20that%20was%20there%20with%20her%20small%20fawn.%20Seeing%20the%20doe%20in%20pain%20and%20her%20fawn%20in%20tears%2C%20I%20felt%20great%20pain.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20my%20determination%20to%20end%20poaching%20began.%20Immediately%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20forest%20department%20and%20met%20the%20then%20field%20director%2C%20Pradeep%20Shukla.%20I%20confessed%20to%20the%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mistry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20senior%20forest%20official%20suggested%20that%20Mistry%20establish%20a%20society%20or%20organisation%20to%20combat%20poaching.%20He%20assured%20him%20that%20the%20forest%20department%20would%20support%20him%20in%20this%20endeavour.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20set%20up%20the%20Bali%20Nature%20and%20Conservation%20Society%20(BNCS)%20later%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20objective%20is%20to%20save%20wildlife%2C%20nature%20and%20the%20people.%20In%20association%20with%20the%20forest%20department%2C%20we%20help%20locals%20acquire%20alternative%20means%20of%20livelihood%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20hunt.%20We%20also%20work%20with%20officials%2C%20conducting%20joint-patrolling%20operations%20to%20stop%20poachers%20from%20hunting%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Mistry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAnil-Mistry-feature-1-1756722014-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anil%20Mistry%20works%20with%20locals%20in%20Sundarbans%2C%20offering%20alternative%20livelihoods%20to%20reduce%20poaching.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAnil-Mistry-feature-1-1756722014-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAnil-Mistry-feature-1-1756722014-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAnil-Mistry-feature-1-1756722014-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAnil-Mistry-feature-1-1756722014-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAnil-Mistry-feature-1-1756722014-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAnil-Mistry-feature-1-1756722014-96x96.jpg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FAnil-Mistry-feature-1-1756722014.jpg%20556w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-494572%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnil%20Mistry%20works%20with%20locals%20in%20Sundarbans%2C%20offering%20alternative%20livelihoods%20to%20reduce%20poaching.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mistry%E2%80%99s%20life%20took%20a%20real%20turn%20when%20he%20met%20with%20Belinda%20Wright%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Society%20of%20India%20(WPSI)%2C%20soon%20after%20setting%20up%20the%20BNCS.%20After%20meeting%20her%20at%20a%20seminar%2C%20he%20was%20given%20a%20permanent%20job%20with%20the%20WPSI%20to%20oversee%20their%20Sundarbans%20chapter%2C%20conduct%20anti-poaching%20activities%20and%20find%20ways%20of%20offering%20locals%20alternative%20means%20of%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMistry%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CLocals%20go%20into%20the%20jungles%20for%20their%20livelihood%E2%80%94fishing%2C%20hunting%2C%20honey%20collection.%20Sometimes%20they%20encounter%20tigers%2C%20which%20are%20in%20their%20natural%20habitat%2C%20seeking%20food.%20Man-animal%20conflict%20is%20inevitable%20under%20such%20circumstances.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20save%20the%20jungle%2C%20you%20have%20to%20reduce%20the%20incidences%20of%20man-animal%20conflict.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20are%20working%20with%20the%20government%20to%20offer%20locals%20alter