e%20provision%20of%20solar%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20concerted%20efforts%20have%20borne%20real%20fruit%20with%20very%20few%20incidents%20of%20poaching%20reported%20from%20the%20Sundarbans.%20What%E2%80%99s%20even%20more%20remarkable%20is%20the%20change%20in%20behaviour.%20Earlier%2C%20if%20a%20tiger%20strayed%20into%20a%20village%2C%20locals%20would%20try%20and%20kill%20it.%20Today%2C%20they%20inform%20the%20forest%20department%20and%20organisations%20like%20BNCS%20and%20WPSI%20to%20help%20them%20rescue%20it%20and%20release%20it%20back%20into%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20far%2C%20Mistry%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20capture%20and%20release%20of%2070%20tigers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20800px)%20100vw%2C%20800px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWorlds-largest-mangrove-forest-sundarban-bangladesh-Royan-Bengal-Tiger-1-1756722116.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Founder%20of%20BNCS%2C%20Anil%20Mistry%20partners%20with%20forest%20officials%20to%20stop%20poaching%20and%20protect%20wildlife.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWorlds-largest-mangrove-forest-sundarban-bangladesh-Royan-Bengal-Tiger-1-1756722116.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWorlds-largest-mangrove-forest-sundarban-bangladesh-Royan-Bengal-Tiger-1-1756722116-300x201.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWorlds-largest-mangrove-forest-sundarban-bangladesh-Royan-Bengal-Tiger-1-1756722116-500x335.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWorlds-largest-mangrove-forest-sundarban-bangladesh-Royan-Bengal-Tiger-1-1756722116-768x515.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWorlds-largest-mangrove-forest-