easy-tips-steps-diy-guide-grow-bag-balcony-terrace-lucknow%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanted%20from%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20may%20take%20about%20seven%20years%20for%20it%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20But%20if%20you%20bring%20a%20grafted%20plant%20from%20the%20nursery%20and%20plant%20it%2C%20you%20will%20start%20getting%20fruits%20in%20about%20three%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhijeet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20gently%20place%20the%20sapling%20in%20the%20prepared%20soil%2C%20ensuring%20roots%20are%20spread%20out.%20Water%20thoroughly%20to%20settle%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ideal%20time%20for%20planting%20is%20June%20to%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4)%20Regular%20care%20and%20monitoring%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20the%20plant%20whenever%20the%20topsoil%20is%20dry.%20Check%20soil%20moisture%20and%20set%20up%20watering%20schedules.%20You%20can%20use%20organic%20pesticides%20like%20neem%20oil%20to%20protect%20from%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5)%20Harvest%20your%20jackfruits%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20before%20your%20plant%20starts%20growing.%20Jackfruit%20trees%20typically%20take%20three%20to%20five%20years%20to%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20following%20these%20tips%2C%20you%20can%20enjoy%20the%20rewarding%20experience%20of%20growing%20your%20jackfruit%20tree%2C%20reaping%20its%20delicious%20and%20nutritious%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStart%20now%2C%20and%20let%20the%20journey%20of%20nurturing%20begin!%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756557000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D493680%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20monsoon%2C%20Immerse%20in%20season%E2%80%99s%20delights%20with%20homegrown%20jackfruit.%20From%20sunlight%20to%20sapling%20care%2C%20cultivate%20t