Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20the%20subject%20of%20open%20defecation%20was%20broached%2C%20the%20villagers%20were%20out%20of%20options%20on%20how%20to%20tackle%20the%20problem.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMaybe%2C%20we%20could%20build%20toilets%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20plausible%20solution%20was%20floated%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20knee-jerk%20reaction%20did%20not%20faze%20Liby%20and%20his%20team%2C%20who%20kept%20dialoguing%20with%20the%20communities%20until%20the%20latter%20agreed%20to%20a%20toilet%20in%20the%20home.%20In%20the%20two%20decades%20that%20followed%2C%20a%20success%20story%20was%20scripted%20across%201%2C500%20villages%3B%20sanitation%20systems%20were%20streamlined%3B%20the%20ripples%20of%20impact%20were%20felt%20across%2098%2C643%20households%20in%20Nayagarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Liby%20learnt%2C%20redefining%20people%E2%80%99s%20appetite%20for%20change%20sometimes%20needed%20more%20than%20empathy.%20It%20needed%20tact%20and%20a%20knack%20for%20looking%20at%20the%20problem%20through%20a%20new%20prism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolving%20social%20challenges%20with%20strategic%20thinking%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20great%20hypothesis%20does%20not%20guarantee%20success.%20You%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20translate%20your%20promises%20into%20a%20vocabulary%20that%20communities%20will%20trust.%20For%20someone%20who%20is%20a)%20foreign%20to%20the%20development%20sector%20and%20b)%20does%20not%20have%20a%20managerial%20bent%20of%20mind%20while%20attempting%20to%20facilitate%20change%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20this%20can%20be%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20solution%20may%20lie%20in%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EExecutive%20MBA%20in%20Development%20Management%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20that%E2%80%99s%20set%20to%20be%20launched%20by%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EAzim%20Premji%20University%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20assure%20professionals%20a%20surer%20footing%20in%20the%20development%20sector%2C%20which%20often%20denies%20an%20easy%20interpretation%20due%20to%20its%20multifaceted%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Eone-year%20full-time%20programme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20professionals%20will%20learn%20concepts%20and%20competencies%20to%20understand%20contemporary%20development%20challenges%20in%20rural%20and%20urban%20India%20%E2%80%94%20thus%20equipping%20them%20to%20strengthen%20the%20organisational%20capacities%20of%20the%20sectors%20in%20which%20they%20are%20placed%20on%20completion%20of%20the%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%E2%80%99s%20a%20good%20time%20to%20pursue%20this%20programme%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20better%20time%20than%20now%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20development%20sector%20is%20witnessing%20a%20renaissance%3B%20its%20current%20value%20stands%20at%20approximately%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20crore.%20The%20sector%20is%20growing%2C%20believes%20Richa%20Govil%2C%20Vice%20Chancellor%20of%20Azim%20Premji%20University%2C%20Bengaluru%20Campus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERicha%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20think%20the%20non-profit%20world%20is%20a%20world%20of%20charity.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20professional%20space%2C%20and%20just%20like%20other%20sectors%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20managers%20here%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20precisely%20what%20the%20Executive%20MBA%20in%20Development%20Management%20is%20geared%20towards%20%E2%80%94%20creating%20managers%20who%20can%20lead%20to%20create%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIntroducing%20a%20leadership%20lens%20to%20social%20development%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrategic%20thinking%20and%20leadership%20are%20vital%20when%20venturing%20into%20the%20fragile%20intersection%20of%20the%20challenges%20that%20baffle%20India%E2%80%99s%20hinterland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERicha%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20pr