on%20according%20to%20the%20CEEW%20study%E2%80%94%20is%20no%20longer%20constrained%20by%20unreliable%20electricity%20access.%20Instead%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F492080%2Frang-de-peer-to-peer-lending-model-of-loans-helps-farmers-purchase-decentralised-renewable-energy-solutions-like-solar-dryers-hydroponics-units%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDRE%20technologies%20are%20being%20viewed%20as%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20Indian%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20potential%20of%20impacting%20three%20crore%20livelihoods.%20And%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20helping%20script%20this%20success%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPowering%20rural%20futures%20with%20solar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20steadily%20being%20propelled%20towards%20a%20sustainable%20future.%C2%A0%20This%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20plummeting%20costs%20of%20solar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dramatic%2095%20percent%20drop%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20solar%20photovoltaic%20modules%20from%20over%20Rs%20200%20per%20watt%20in%202010%20to%20under%20Rs%209%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20empowering%20people%20in%20rural%20India%20through%20solar%20powered%20atta%20chakkis%20that%20help%20them%20turn%20to%20entrepreneurship%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-1756464636-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-493600%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20empowering%20people%20in%20rural%20India%20through%20solar-powered%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakkis%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20help%20them%20turn%20to%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Jain%2C%20Fellow%20and%20Director%2C%20Green%20Economy%20and%20Impact%20Innovations%2C%20CEEW%2C%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20this%20plunge%20in%20prices%20is%20making%20green%20applications%20affordable.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20started%20realising%20that%20solar%20can%20be%20harnessed%20for%20so%20many%20other%20productive%20applications%20beyond%20consumptive%20use%20in%20rural%20areas.%20The%20missing%20gap%20was%20how%20to%20make%20these%20appliances%20efficient%3B%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20trying%20to%20solve%20for%20this%20by%20creating%20energy-efficient%20appliances.%E2%80%9D%20These%20appliances%20are%20now%20creating%20quite%20a%20stir%20in%20the%20villages%20where%20they%20are%20being%20introduced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20plausible%20reason%20could%20be%20the%20increased%20earnings%20following%20DRE%20tech%20adoption.%20As%20pointed%20out%20by%20a%20CEEW%20report%2C%2090%20percent%20of%20those%20who%20adopted%20a%20DRE%20solution%20reported%20income%20growth%2C%20typically%20achieving%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20INR%2040%2C000%20(with%20an%20average%20usage%20of%20eight%20months)%2C%20a%2033%20percent%20increase%20compared%20to%20their%20baseline%20earnings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20earnings%20are%20one%20side%20of%20the%20story%2C%20the%20other%20side%20is